	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey Guys!
<br />
<br />I've heard Tepples suggest people make a game design document but I never found a template for one.
<br />
<br />Anyone heard of such a thing?  I tried the forum search to no avail.  Google comes up with some very generic looking docs but is there something more specific for consoles?
<br />
<br />I'm thinking of making an action/adventure RPG with heavy inspiration from Super Pitfall.  Yes, I know some wouldn't see where "inspiration" and Super Pitfall meet, but, still!
<br />
<br />Thanks in advance for any guidance in this <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
