	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Try writing the game's manual. Then try writing the strategy guide. You won't be able to go into minute detail at first because your ideas haven't been play-tested, but at least describe what you can.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


