		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You're welcome. It's not too qualitatively different from the flow you say you currently use, just a bit more detail in the "sketch out gameplay on paper" step. The more you have on paper, the easier it will be to get other members of your team on the same page.
<br />
<br />Try looking through the revision history of <a href="http://pineight.com/mw/index.php?title=Thwaite" class="postlink">the page about my nesdevcompo entry</a>.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
