		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I can easily create grids in TeX if you want it, of any pitch, with any kinds of row or column headers, different thicknesses of lines, all of that stuff. I can even make the NES PPU background plan form using TeX, and you could even write the entire document using TeX, or some "Literate NES" program.

		

		</td>
